=== 數據收集 ===
CCleaner 5.45的Active System Monitoring組件發布後，包含了一個數據收集模塊，該模塊無需計算機所有者的同意即可從計算機收集信息。 Piriform聲稱它沒有收集個人身份信息。 經過批評後，儘管默認情況下仍啟用數據收集，但以後的版本允許用戶分別控制數據收集。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sensorstechforum.com/ccleaner-v5-45-data-collection/|title=CCleaner v5.45 Introduces Data Collection with No Way to Opt-Out|website=Sensors Tech Forum|date=3 August 2018|author=Milena Dimitrova|accessdate=14 October 2018|archive-date=2019-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190412181802/https://sensorstechforum.com/ccleaner-v5-45-data-collection/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.ccleaner.com/news/release-announcements/2018/8/30/ccleaner-v5466652 |title=CCleaner v5.46.6652 |website=CCleaner.com |date=30 August 2018 |author= |accessdate=14 October 2018 |archive-date=2020-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200224223059/http://www.ccleaner.com/news/release-announcements/2018/8/30/ccleaner-v5466652 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.zdnet.com/article/cc-cleaner-provokes-fury-over-active-monitoring/|title=CCleaner provokes fury over Active Monitoring, user data collection|last=Osborne|first=Charlie|website=ZDNet|language=en|access-date=2019-06-28|archive-date=2019-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190406180209/https://www.zdnet.com/article/cc-cleaner-provokes-fury-over-active-monitoring/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://support.piriform.com/hc/en-us/articles/360010631671-I-m-using-CCleaner-v5-45-Why-is-Active-Monitoring-still-on-when-I-have-switched-it-off-|title=I'm using CCleaner v5.45. Why is Active Monitoring still on when I have switched it off?|website=Piriform Support|date=8 October 2018|author=|accessdate=14 October 2018|archive-date=2018-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181014165727/https://support.piriform.com/hc/en-us/articles/360010631671-I-m-using-CCleaner-v5-45-Why-is-Active-Monitoring-still-on-when-I-have-switched-it-off-|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 捆綁軟件 ===
據報導，在2018年12月，安裝CCleaner的用戶也將在未經其許可的情況下安裝[[Avast|Avast]]防病毒軟件，TechSpot聲稱這可以說使CCleaner並不比它應該防禦的惡意軟件更好。 Piriform否認了這一點。<ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.techspot.com/news/77949-ccleaner-could-install-avast-anti-virus-without-permission.html|title= CCleaner may be installing Avast anti-virus without your permission|website= TechSpot|date= 19 December 2018|author= David Matthews|accessdate= 20 January 2019|archive-date= 2019-10-18|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20191018165019/https://www.techspot.com/news/77949-ccleaner-could-install-avast-anti-virus-without-permission.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>

== 惡意軟件感染 ==
在Piriform被Avast收購後，2017年9月12日，Piriform的母公司[[Avast|Avast]]發現同年8月釋出的CCleaner版本v5.33.6162和CCleaner Cloud 版本v1.07.3191被植入[[特洛伊木马_(电脑)|特洛伊木马]]可以被安裝[[軟體後門|軟體後門]]，约227万用户计算机已遭感染，[[駭客|駭客]]可能以此遠端控制32位系统的计算机。40台被感染的計算機收到了第二階段有效負載，這些負載似乎針對的是科技公司三星，索尼，華碩，英特爾，VMWare，O2，新加坡電信，高素曼，Dyn，中華電信和富士通<ref>{{cite web|url=https://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2017/09/ccleaner-backdoor-infecting-millions-delivered-mystery-payload-to-40-pcs/|title=CCleaner backdoor infecting millions delivered mystery payload to 40 PCs|author=Dan Goodin|date=2017-09-25|website=Ars Technica|accessdate=2020-05-22|archive-date=2020-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200521095002/https://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2017/09/ccleaner-backdoor-infecting-millions-delivered-mystery-payload-to-40-pcs/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ncsc">{{cite web|url=https://www.dni.gov/files/NCSC/documents/news/20180724-economic-espionage-pub.pdf|title=Foreign Economic Espionage in Cyberspace|date=2018-07-24|website=CIA|accessdate=2020-05-22|archive-date=2020-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200415170050/https://www.dni.gov/files/NCSC/documents/news/20180724-economic-espionage-pub.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該公司已緊急更新版本並呼籲使用者盡速更新。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.inside.com.tw/article/10552-avast-ccleaner-gets-hit-by-a-nasty-malware-infection |title=系統清理軟體CCleaner被駭 可能控制你的電腦 |accessdate=2019-03-23 |archive-date=2019-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190323133440/https://www.inside.com.tw/article/10552-avast-ccleaner-gets-hit-by-a-nasty-malware-infection |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-security-avast/hackers-compromised-free-ccleaner-software-avasts-piriform-says-idUSKCN1BT0R9|title=Hackers compromised free CCleaner software, Avast's Piriform says|accessdate=2017年9月20日|author=Joseph Menn|date=2017年9月18日|publisher=reuters|archive-date=2017年9月19日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170919234312/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-security-avast/hackers-compromised-free-ccleaner-software-avasts-piriform-says-idUSKCN1BT0R9|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://techcrunch.com/2017/09/18/avast-reckons-ccleaner-malware-infected-2-27m-users/|title=Avast reckons CCleaner malware infected 2.27M users|accessdate=2017年9月20日|author=Natasha Lomas|date=|publisher=techcrunch|archive-date=2017年9月19日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170919234637/https://techcrunch.com/2017/09/18/avast-reckons-ccleaner-malware-infected-2-27m-users/|dead-url=no}}</ref>9月13日，Piriform發布了沒有惡意代碼的CCleaner 5.34和CCleaner Cloud 1.07.3191<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pcmag.com/review/351824/ccleaner-professional-plus|title=CCleaner Professional Plus|last1=Rubenking|first1=By Jeffrey L. Wilson and Neil J.|last2=September 19|first2=2017 3:15PM EST|website=PCMAG|last3=September 19|first3=2017|accessdate=2020-05-22|archive-date=2019-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191004130355/https://www.pcmag.com/review/351824/ccleaner-professional-plus|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2019年10月21日，Avast披露了第二個安全漏洞，在此期間，黑客再次嘗試將惡意軟件插入CCleaner版本中。 該嘗試未成功<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.zdnet.com/article/avast-says-hackers-breached-internal-network-through-compromised-vpn-profile/|title=Avast says hackers breached internal network through compromised VPN profile|last=Cimpanu|first=Catalin|website=ZDNet|language=en|access-date=2019-10-21|archive-date=2019-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191021142422/https://www.zdnet.com/article/avast-says-hackers-breached-internal-network-through-compromised-vpn-profile/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

